msgstr "``openvpn``: tunnel OpenVPN"

#: ../../port_forward.rst:76 d3167333d38d4976b611c5b54d749473
msgid "``rwopenvpn``: OpenVPN Road Warrior"
msgstr "``rwopenvpn``: OpenVPN Road Warrior"

#: ../../port_forward.rst:78 52f87efa96844a0eaf1344f5f114846e
msgid ""
"If multiple tunnels or networks are present, all must be included in their "
"respective zones."
msgstr ""
"Se sono presenti più tunnel o reti, tutti devono essere inclusi nelle "
"rispettive zone."

